                <![CDATA[<p>第 96 屆奧斯卡頒獎禮於香港時間今早在美國加州洛杉磯杜比劇院完滿落幕。今年競爭毫無懸念，由 Cillian Murphy 憑《奧本海默》勇奪影帝，Emma Stone 憑《可憐的東西》奪得影后殊榮。《奧本海默》更獲得 13 項大獎提名，最終橫掃 7 獎，成為今屆奪得最多奧斯卡獎項的大贏家。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223614" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/maxresdefault3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/maxresdefault3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/maxresdefault3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 最佳電影︰《奧本海默》Oppenheimer</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223619" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/christophernolanwins-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/christophernolanwins-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/christophernolanwins.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 最佳導演：《奧本海默》Christopher Nolan</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223621" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/cillianmurphywinsbes-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/cillianmurphywinsbes-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/cillianmurphywinsbes.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 最佳男主角：《奧本海默》Cillian Murphy</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223622" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/emmastonewinsbestact-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/emmastonewinsbestact-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/emmastonewinsbestact.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 最佳女主角：《可憐的東西》Emma Stone</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223624" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/robertdowneyjrwinsbe-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/robertdowneyjrwinsbe-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/robertdowneyjrwinsbe.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 最佳男配角：《奧本海默》Robert Downey Jr.</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223627" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/davinejoyrandolphwin-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/davinejoyrandolphwin-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/davinejoyrandolphwin.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 最佳女配角：《滯留生》Da&#8217;Vine Joy Randolph</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223630" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/unwire-1710133288-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/unwire-1710133288-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/unwire-1710133288.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 最佳國際影片：《特權樂園》The Zone of Interest</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223634" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fdb7f331b64bd41c9556-694x339.jpg" alt="" width="69